<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Indigestible -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_Indigestible.label>不可消化</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_Indigestible.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn is immune to digestion. Not immune to bullets, blades, explosions, or even external acid sprays, but certainly immune to digestion. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_Indigestible.description>这个角色完全不会被消化。子弹、刀剑、爆炸、甚至泼到身上的强酸都能要他的命，唯独消化液对他无可奈何。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_Indigestible.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Instant digestion -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_InstantDigestion.label>瞬间消化</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_InstantDigestion.label>
  <!-- EN: Only the pawn-tron reduces an entire preything into soup-like homogenate in 30 seconds. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_InstantDigestion.description>这个角色能做到——把一整只猎物在30秒内化为汤汁般的匀浆。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_InstantDigestion.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Melty -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_Bad.label>易溶体质</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_Bad.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn melts under acid easily and won't last more than half as long in a hostile belly as most prey. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_Bad.description>这个角色在酸液里溶解得飞快，落入敌胃后存活时间还不到普通猎物的一半。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_Bad.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Acid-resistant -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_Good.label>耐酸体质</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_Good.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn resists digestion well, and will last about twice as long as most prey in a hostile belly. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_Good.description>这个角色对消化液有不错的抵抗力，被困在敌胃里时，存活时间大约是普通猎物的两倍。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_Good.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Normal acid resistance -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_Normal.label>普通耐酸</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_Normal.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn is digested as easily as anyone else. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_Normal.description>这个角色的耐酸能力和普通人没什么两样，该化还是得化。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_Normal.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Cotton candy -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_VeryBad.label>入口即化</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_VeryBad.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn falls apart in stomach acid like cotton candy, and doesn't fare any better in other organs. They have maybe a quarter of the time to escape as normal prey. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_VeryBad.description>这个角色在胃酸里就像棉花糖遇水——瞬间就散架了，到了其他消化器官里也好不到哪去。他们能用来逃命的时间，大概只有普通猎物的四分之一。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_VeryBad.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Acid-proof -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_VeryGood.label>强酸抗性</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_VeryGood.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn is very difficult to digest. Not impossible, but it'll take a while; about four times as long as most prey. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_VeryGood.description>这个角色极难被消化——倒也不是完全消化不掉，只是需要相当长的时间，大概是普通猎物的四倍之久。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionResistance_VeryGood.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Weak acid -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Bad.label>弱酸胃液</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Bad.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn takes about twice as long to digest live meals as most predators. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Bad.description>这个角色消化活体猎物的速度比大多数捕食者慢了一倍，大概需要两倍的时间才能搞定一顿饭。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Bad.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Godlike Digestion -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Godlike.label>神之消化</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Godlike.label>
  <!-- EN: Whether due to magic or a technology that's not yet understood, this pawn's digestive abilities are in a class of their own, capable of liquifying an entire Thrumbo in minutes. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Godlike.description>无论是魔法还是某种未知科技在起作用，这个角色的消化能力都堪称超凡脱俗——几分钟内就能把一整只敲击兽化为液态。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Godlike.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Potent acid -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Good.label>强效胃酸</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Good.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn can digest prey about twice as fast as most predators. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Good.description>这个角色消化猎物的速度比大多数捕食者快上一倍，效率惊人。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Good.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Normal acid strength -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Normal.label>普通胃酸</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Normal.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn digests prey at a normal speed. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Normal.description>这个角色的消化速度属于正常水平，不快也不慢。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_Normal.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Watery acid -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_VeryBad.label>稀薄胃酸</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_VeryBad.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn takes about four times as long to digest prey as most predators. This pawn's food is liable to die of boredom before dying of melting. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_VeryBad.description>这个角色消化猎物的速度慢得离谱，是大多数捕食者的四倍之久。照这个速度，猎物怕是还没被融化，就先在胃里等得无聊死了。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_VeryBad.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Scouring acid -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_VeryGood.label>强蚀胃酸</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_VeryGood.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn can turn prey into nutrient soup in the blink of an eye- -or, at least, four times as fast as most predators. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_VeryGood.description>这个角色能在眨眼之间把猎物化为营养浓汤——至少，速度是大多数捕食者的四倍。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DigestionStrength_VeryGood.description>
  
</LanguageData>